sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Mahasiswa
    participant S as Sistem Akademik
    participant D as Dosen PA
    participant DB as Database

    M->>S: Submit KRS
    S->>DB: Ambil Data KRS & Mata Kuliah
    DB-->>S: Data KRS

    S->>S: Cek Prasyarat
    S->>S: Cek SKS Maksimal (<= 24)
    S->>S: Cek Jadwal Bentrok

    alt Validasi Gagal
        S-->>M: KRS Ditolak (Pesan Error)
    else Validasi Lolos
        S->>DB: Simpan Status KRS (Pending)
        DB-->>S: Konfirmasi
        S-->>M: Status KRS = Pending Approval
        S-->>D: Notifikasi Persetujuan KRS
    end
